    <text>
        <body>
            <div xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Imre Kálnai (Augsburg, 13 October 1530)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1"> Oláh cannot but be surprised how fickle rulers are. The
                            King promised him in solemn words that as soon as there was a vacancy,
                            he would receive a bishopric; now he still gave it to someone else.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb facs="https://www.eleveltar.hu/kereso-portlet/spring/digitalcontent/getcontent/preservica/32A39862-4350-416D-AC4A-0E2126258D4A
                    "/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Ad <persName>Emericum Kalnay</persName>.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Non possum non conqueri de temporum malignitate principumque
                    inconstantia. Princeps meus <del corresp="Olahus">clementissimus</del>
                    temporibus superioribus me hanc certe gratiam nihil petente promiserat, et non
                    vanis sed sollennibus verbis, uti principum est iusiurandum, in verbo suo regio
                    promiserat, inquam, se mihi sacerdotium illud qualecumque in Hungaria nostra
                    primitus vacaret collaturum. Nunc vacavit unus item alter episcopatus, utrumque
                    non servans promissionem, alteri <del corresp="Olahus">conferre
                        cogitat</del><add corresp="Olahus" type="corr">contulit</add>; vide, quanta
                    sit constantia eorum, qui constantiae exemplum aliis praebere deberent. Haec non
                    mea causa scribo, contentus enim ita vivam, semper fui mea sorte, quae dum pax
                    est, non est inter alias inferior, sed vicem eorum doleo, qui sunt tam varii,
                    cum constantes esse deberent. Vale.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Ex <placeName>Augusta</placeName> XIII. Octobris MDXXX.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
